---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Georgia Nut — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Family-owned since 1945, Georgia Nut deployed the first robot in its 75-year history with Formic — a collaborative palletizer handling up to 10 cases a minute, with zero line shutdowns since."
  ogTitle="Georgia Nut — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="First robot in company history · 10 cases/min · zero shutdowns"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/georgia-nut" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Georgia Nut
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Georgia Nut</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Georgia Nut and Formic Deploy First Robot in Company's History</h1>
    <p class="lede">Family-owned since 1945, Georgia Nut put the first robot in its 75-year history on the floor with Formic — a collaborative palletizer handling up to 10 cases a minute, with zero line shutdowns since.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/georgia-nut-hero.jpg" alt="Georgia Nut collaborative palletizing robot" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Georgia Nut · first robot deployed</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1945</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Ownership</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Family-owned</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">In business</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">75+ years</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Confections & contract mfg</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Milestone</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">First robot in company history</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>First robot, <em>after 75 years</em>.</h2>
      <p>Georgia Nut, founded in 1945 and family-owned for 75+ years, faced a severe labor shortage against high order volumes — with no prior automation experience anywhere in the building. Formic's robotics-as-a-service model is what made saying yes to that first robot possible.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>75+ years, family-owned</li>
        <li>Severe labor shortage against high order volumes</li>
        <li>No prior automation experience</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/georgia-nut-2.jpg" alt="Georgia Nut palletizing robot at end of line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Collaborative palletizer</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic collaborative palletizing system" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Re-task in &lt;30 min</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>A cobot that <em>re-tasks in minutes</em>.</h2>
      <p>With implementation partner Sourcelink Solutions, Formic deployed a Yaskawa Motoman HC20 collaborative robot — custom end-of-arm tool, touch-screen operator interface, safety scanners, and stand wheels — that re-tasks in under 30 minutes with a floor jack. Formic covered equipment procurement, custom engineering, installation costs, and uptime guarantees.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Yaskawa Motoman HC20 cobot with custom tooling</li>
        <li>Re-tasks in under 30 minutes with a floor jack</li>
        <li>Formic covers procurement, engineering, and uptime</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"Formic has some skin in the game, because they're only getting incentivized when the machine is running, not when it's down."</blockquote>
      <cite>Matt Neuman · Distribution & Packaging Manager, Georgia Nut</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Impact</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Up to 10 cases a minute. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Zero shutdowns.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">10</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Cases per minute</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">2</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Boxes picked at once</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">0</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Line shutdowns since</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Deploy your <em>first robot</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
